      },
      "date": "2013-12-16 14:05:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nAndreas I figured out why the aruthorship was changing. There are two ways a patch can be submitted. One is git apply and the other git am. Reading the docs I see now that git apply can change the aruthorship but git am doesn't.Of course to submit with git am the patch has to be in proper format.I have been using git apply but now I will switch over. This should be pointed out on the contributor page.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
